dcterms:description: A novel image-text dataset imbued with three typical implicit concepts (i.e., QR codes, watermarks, and text), reflecting real-life situations where implicit concepts are easily injected.
dcterms:title: Implicit Concept Dataset (ICD)

dcterms:creator: J.N.M. Pinkney
dcterms:description: A dataset containing image-text pairs with QR codes embedded in 25% of the images, sourced from the Pokemon dataset.
dcterms:title: ICD-QR

dcterms:creator: S. Changpinyo
P. Sharma

dcterms:description: A dataset sourced from CC12M, containing images with watermarks, with half of the images including watermarks.
dcterms:title: ICD-Watermark

dcterms:description: A dataset from LAION containing images with text, where 100% of the training images incorporate text.
dcterms:title: ICD-Text
